This works with the game at the following link: https://gameforge.com/en-US/littlegames/magic-piano-tiles/#
Be sure to full screen your game for this to work properly.

Adjust the pixel placements to your own, this will change if you are not using a 2560x1440p monitor.

It is better to run this script in a python3 shell otherwise it won't work as written, also better performance when using IDLE.


Links to documentations:

https://pyautogui.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html

https://pypi.org/project/keyboard/

https://docs.python.org/3/library/time.html